1
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:11,200
When Brother Gang is on the job, he's worth two men.

2
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:13,720
Uncle Tian.

3
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:16,160
Gangzi! Isn't that Gangzi?

4
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:18,210
Uncle Tian! Uncle Tian!

5
00:01:18,240 --> 00:01:20,880
You must know Qiangzi and Yongzi, right?

6
00:01:20,880 --> 00:01:22,400
We're from the same village.

7
00:01:22,400 --> 00:01:24,920
It's true we haven't done this kind of work before.

8
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:27,000
In the future, if you need anything, just say the word.

9
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:27,720
No problem.

10
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:30,120
This job isn't very difficult.

11
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:33,000
Just make sure to patrol your assigned mining areas properly.

12
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:33,440
That's all.

13
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:35,160
Alright. Take it seriously.

14
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:35,720
Don't worry.

15
00:01:35,720 --> 00:01:37,320
If anything happens, I'm holding you accountable.

16
00:01:37,320 --> 00:01:38,080
You got it.

17
00:01:43,880 --> 00:01:46,120
You saw what happened at the union yesterday, right?

18
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:48,479
Situ Hongtang has found a helper now.

19
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:51,600
She's using Yang Gang as her mouthpiece

20
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:55,979
to incite the workers to accept the restructuring.

21
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,600
Do you know what to do?

22
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:02,560
Yes.

23
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,640
Yang Gang is illegally mining copper.

24
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:07,300
He relies on Wu Qiang from the village to sell it.

25
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:10,840
Tell the guys below.

26
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:13,970
No one is allowed to buy Yang Gang's goods.

27
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,610
If anyone buys from him,

28
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:18,040
they are going against me, Xiao Tianman.

29
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:19,300
Don't worry, Mr. Xiao.

30
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:22,120
We've got a hold on Yang Gang's money supply.

31
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:24,680
He definitely won't survive in Dayang Village.

32
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:26,140
I'll handle it right away.

33
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:33,280
Brother Gang, I think I've figured it out.

34
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:34,810
You used your charms on her.

35
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:36,920
With Situ Hongtang as our backer,

36
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,560
we can roam the mines as we please.

37
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,720
What do you mean, charms?

38
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,640
Do you know what this is called?

39
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:45,880
It's called 'feinting east, striking west'.

40
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:46,640
Get it?

41
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:47,720
Feint...

42
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,040
Strike... we work.

43
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:49,840
West.

44
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:04,880
Brother Gang, Mr. Xiao has spoken.

45
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:06,880
I really can't buy your ore anymore.

46
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:11,280
Mr. Wu, please do me a favor.

47
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:13,480
I'll take twenty, you take eighty.

48
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:17,320
Even if you took ten and I took ninety, I can't.

49
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:18,079
If I buy your ore again,

50
00:03:18,079 --> 00:03:19,480
I'll be out of business.

51
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:26,960
Brother Gang.

52
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:29,650
Please don't make this hard for me.

53
00:03:33,320 --> 00:03:34,850
Sorry to bother you, Mr. Wu.

54
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:36,640
Let's go.

55
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:53,360
Gangzi.

56
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:56,820
If it really doesn't work out, just let it be.

57
00:03:57,800 --> 00:04:00,720
Cancer treatment is a bottomless pit.

58
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:04,120
Although I don't have a biological son,

59
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:05,480
I raised you,

60
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,660
and seeing how filial you are,

61
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,320
I am satisfied.

62
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:16,279
I promise I won't help Shanshui Group anymore.

63
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,800
I just feel bad for you.

64
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,079
I don't want you to be too tired.

65
00:04:19,079 --> 00:04:20,320
We're not tired.

66
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,440
We're not tired, right?

67
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:23,000
Not at all. Godmother, don't say that.

68
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:23,930
We're not tired.

69
00:04:24,280 --> 00:04:26,440
Mom, just rest easy.

70
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:28,160
Don't worry, we're all here.

71
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:30,000
We're all here, Godmother.

72
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:39,720
Brother, the payment to Sun is due tomorrow.

73
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,520
Do we have a plan?

74
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:16,400
Brother, this...

75
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:20,920
Take this and pawn it. It should be enough.

76
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:23,600
Brother, I can't take this.

77
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:27,500
This is the only memento Godfather left you.

78
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:28,960
And...

79
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:33,560
this might be the last of the money to save Godmother's life.

80
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,380
I really can't take it.

81
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:38,140
It's okay. Take it.

82
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:41,960
If I can't pay it back,

83
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:44,200
it's just a finger, right?

84
00:05:46,159 --> 00:05:47,220
I'll give it to him.

85
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,159
Qiangzi, Qiangzi!

86
00:05:49,159 --> 00:05:49,920
Brother!

87
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,600
I still have a way.

88
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:56,440
What can you do?

89
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,440
What can you possibly do?

90
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,120
Sit down first. Sit down.

91
00:06:05,080 --> 00:06:07,140
What kind of solution could you have?

92
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,840
Brother Gang, just take it back.

93
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,260
This is Godmother's life-saving money.

94
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:26,280
Yongzi and I were saving this for our wedding.

95
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:29,720
Brother Qiang, use it for the emergency.

96
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:40,440
Yongzi and I can just get married a few years later. Right?

97
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:41,760
Besides,

98
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:44,000
I believe you guys will definitely make big money.

99
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,260
Just take it and use it.

100
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,800
I can't use this money.

101
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:53,490
Just consider it a loan from us.

102
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,080
Take it.

103
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:12,480
Mr. Xiao, Yang Gang is here. He insists on seeing you.

104
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:15,640
What is he doing here?

105
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:18,720
He says he has something important to tell you.

106
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:19,980
What important thing?

107
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:22,220
He wants to tell you in person.

108
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:26,490
This Yang Gang is too funny.

109
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:29,720
I haven't even settled the score for when he kidnapped me last time.

110
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,520
And now he delivers himself to my doorstep.

111
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:33,480
Fine. Let him in.

112
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:38,080
Please.

113
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:49,080
Isn't this the miner representative of Shanshui Group,

114
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:50,360
Mr. Yang Gang?

115
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,440
What brings you here?

116
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:55,600
Well, Mr. Xiao,

117
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:58,960
I came here this time to beg you

118
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:00,920
to do me a favor.

119
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,530
Did I hear that right, Mr. Yang?

120
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:06,960
Begging me for a favor?

121
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,000
Yes.

122
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:11,400
What is it?

123
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:18,440
Could you buy some ore from me?

124
00:08:20,960 --> 00:08:22,720
Nobody's buying your ore, huh?

125
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,610
Mr. Yang, you...

126
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:26,720
You've always been so capable.

127
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:28,760
You even dared to kidnap me.

128
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:30,480
And now you need to beg me?

129
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:31,680
Mr. Xiao, I...

130
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:35,720
I really hope you can help me out.

131
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:38,200
Because no one in Dayang Village dares to buy my ore.

132
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:40,799
And my mom is about to have surgery soon.

133
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:42,460
I really have no other choice.

134
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:44,720
You have parents too.

135
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:46,200
You should understand.

136
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,480
Filial piety comes first.

137
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,560
Don't provoke me.

138
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:51,920
What does your mother's illness have to do with me?

139
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:56,040
By the way,

140
00:08:56,040 --> 00:08:57,720
your Shanshui Group...

141
00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:01,200
They don't know about you stealing and selling ore, do they?

142
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,520
If they found out,

143
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:05,440
what do you think they would do to you?

144
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,240
Mr. Xiao.

145
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:08,680
First of all, I was never part of Shanshui Group.

146
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:09,680
I never was.

147
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:13,440
When I helped Situ Hongtang back then,

148
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,080
I just thought

149
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:17,600
she might bring benefits to our Dayang Village mine.

150
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,040
Or...

151
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:19,840
So you do know you're not part of Shanshui Group.

152
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:20,840
Right, Yang Gang?

153
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,000
Also,

154
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,560
how did you determine that Situ Hongtang

155
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:28,560
was doing it for the good of the people in Dayang Village?

156
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:29,680
How did you judge that?

157
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:30,740
I can't judge that.

158
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,530
But rest assured, Mr. Xiao.

159
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:35,180
I promise I won't help Shanshui Group again.

160
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,080
So,

161
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:42,820
Mr. Xiao, I'm really at the end of my rope.

162
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,800
I really have no other choice.

163
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:46,600
If you help me this one time,

164
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,560
whatever you need in the future,

165
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:51,020
just say the word to the three of us brothers.

166
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:53,250
We'd go through fire and water for you.

167
00:09:55,160 --> 00:09:55,960
Okay?

168
00:09:59,400 --> 00:10:00,200
Sit.

169
00:10:11,680 --> 00:10:12,480
Yang Gang.

170
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:15,800
I'm a businessman.

171
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:18,860
Businessmen believe in mutual benefit, right?

172
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:21,640
I can have my people buy your ore.

173
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:27,400
But on the condition that you do me a favor.

174
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,280
Don't be so reserved.

175
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:39,160
We're all on the same side now.

176
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:39,880
Mr. Xiao.

177
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:43,260
You were looking for me? You're here, Liao Fei. Sit.

178
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:45,980
Exhausted, right?

179
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,040
Yeah.

180
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:50,200
Thanks for the hard work, brother.

181
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:52,040
You've been working overtime these past few days,

182
00:10:52,040 --> 00:10:53,400
trying to wash more ore.

183
00:10:53,640 --> 00:10:54,840
It's been hard on you.

184
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:58,130
No need for introductions,

185
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,700
we all know each other.

186
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:02,180
I called you here today

187
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:04,130
to discuss something with you.

188
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:06,760
Gangzi

189
00:11:07,800 --> 00:11:09,600
urgently needs money right now.

190
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:11,440
Something happened at home.

191
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:13,280
His mom needs medical treatment.

192
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:14,320
So I was thinking,

193
00:11:14,760 --> 00:11:16,040
why not let Gangzi

194
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:18,000
wash ore with you?

195
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:22,920
Right. Things have been really...

196
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,260
difficult lately.

197
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:26,320
I also feel this is a bit...

198
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:27,400
a bit unfair.

199
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,280
But I really have no choice.

200
00:11:29,280 --> 00:11:30,120
But I promise,

201
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:32,800
once I scrape together enough for my mom's bills,

202
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:34,130
I'll quit immediately.

203
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:36,770
I really appreciate Mr. Xiao for this.

204
00:11:37,880 --> 00:11:38,740
Don't say that.

205
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:41,520
Fei will definitely understand, right?

206
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:43,760
We've been neighbors for so many years.

207
00:11:43,760 --> 00:11:45,420
Everyone falls on hard times.

208
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:47,240
And Fei, let me tell you,

209
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:48,480
Gangzi is very loyal.

210
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:51,960
He's the best ore washer in Dayang Village.

211
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:54,020
We don't need to discuss that, right?

212
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:56,060
And the price he gave me this time,

213
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:58,280
is just this much.
